layers.characters: We have a landing page design that needs to be converted into the Elementor Pro. The design consists of 5 to 6 sections with a form. Whenever there's a row of circles, these should work as tabs. The form consists of a couple of steps with questions until the user can enter his data. The answers should be saved - for example in hidden form fields. About the working of form, Users will access the form by clicking on the CTA button "Wachtumsanalyse starten!". Then the website scrolls down to the form. It has a progress bar, which increases after each step. After a user clicks on an answer button, the next question slides in from the right. In the end, all answers and the form data (name, e-mail, phone number) should be sent to an e-mail address. We are using WP Contact Form 7, maybe we can reuse this. Please contact so that I can share the design.
